# Compiled WASM binaries are generated by:
#   python -m rufus_edge.sidecar.build_wasm
#
# The apply_config.wasm binary is committed here after compilation
# so edge devices receive it via ETag config push without build tooling.
#
# To compile:
#   pip install py2wasm
#   python -m rufus_edge.sidecar.build_wasm
